  <summary>6/7/2001--Introduced.
Reservist VA Home Loan Fairness Act of 2001 - Prescribes uniform fees for members of the Selected Reserve and veterans eligible through qualifying active duty service for home loans guaranteed, insured, or made through the Department of Veterans Affairs (currently, separate fees apply to active duty veterans and reservists).</summary>
